              "free_text": [
                " Cross-section",
                "  for gamma-rays with energy 0.84 MeV at inelastic",
                "  scattering of neutrons by iron at 1.2 MeV was taken",
                "  from R.M.Kiehn, G.Goodman.Phys.Rev.,95,989,1954,",
                "  I.Van Loef,D.Lind. Phys.Rev.,101,103,1956 and",
                "  D.Hughes,R.B.Shwartz Neutron Cross Sections,",
                "  BNL-325,1958 and is given in COMMON  section .",
                "        For calibration of energy-scale of gammas",
                "gamma-sources Na-22 (gamma-energies 0.511 and",
                "1.280 MeV),Na-24 (1.380 and 2.750 MeV),Co-60 (1.170",
                "and 1.332 MeV),Zn-65 (0.511 and 1.120 MeV), Y-88(0.908",
                "and 1.850 MeV),Sb-124(0.603,1.380,1.690,2.090 MeV),",
                "Cs-137 (0.661 MeV) were used."
              ]
